v0.3.0
------
- the inverse option allows you to invert the colors of the image

- the resize-array was added to resize the image

- the reset option allows you to reset all effects and arrays


v0.2.0
------
- the moveImg-array was added to move the image in its canvas

- the canvasWidthExt and canvasHeightExt values got replaced by the canvasExt-array
		[canvasWidthExt, canvasHeight]


v0.1.1
------
- imgSrc, imgWidth, imgHeight are now part of the (hidden) "variables"-object and "img" is
		the new option in "options", where "img" is an array ([imgSrc, imgWidth, imgHeight]).

- the image is now shown as soon as it's loaded and stored in the imgArray for faster reuse.


v.0.1.0
-------
- with a big bang the magic happend